    "name": "ZERO Sievert",
    "steam_appid": 1782120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/2b3e4d3636d14c30c6bdbe09c29d0074.poster.avif?t=1763116403\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/2b3e4d3636d14c30c6bdbe09c29d0074.webm?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/2b3e4d3636d14c30c6bdbe09c29d0074.mp4?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界已经毁灭。《Zero Sievert》的背景设定在虚构的东欧末世，你将在多个地区搜刮装备。作为行动基地的地堡内有商人、改装站以及自定区域，助力你在荒野的探险之旅。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，一旦走出地堡踏入荒野，周遭将不再安全。游戏包含六大地图，你的初始装备只有一把枪和一瓶水，需要靠自己去搜寻物品，干掉土匪。最重要的是，活着回来。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请注意，当地的某些野生动物可能会受到核沉降物的影响…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/4c36fff43cd0af965ee17bd4625e178f.poster.avif?t=1763116403\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/4c36fff43cd0af965ee17bd4625e178f.webm?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/4c36fff43cd0af965ee17bd4625e178f.mp4?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索荒地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >系统生成的地图带来了不一样的体验，每次前往森林、商场或临时营地都有不一样的路线，其中包括不断变化的天气、藏身点、战利品地点和路线布局。深入探索六张地图，试着找出每张地图的规则秘密。安全回归，祝你每次都有别样收获。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/e48aee469638f340d1cbfa67af4f94b3.poster.avif?t=1763116403\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/e48aee469638f340d1cbfa67af4f94b3.webm?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/e48aee469638f340d1cbfa67af4f94b3.mp4?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全面武器改装</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以最适合你玩法的方式进行狩猎。超过50种独特的枪械和150种模组组装，助你在《Zero Sievert》的荒原上所向披靡。创造适合你的风格，打造强力的武器，成为终极猎人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/dabdaa0a125229404e5d759438632135.poster.avif?t=1763116403\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/dabdaa0a125229404e5d759438632135.webm?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >磨砺装备，尽展技能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在严酷的荒原中生存，你将获得经验，磨练技能，并解锁新的途径，成长为致命猎人。武器技能系统可升级各种武器类型，提高诸如装填速度、伤害、移动速度等属性，甚至解锁针对每种武器量身定制的独特技能。除了武器经验，你作为猎人本身也能升级，获得独特的专长。它们将助力你闯荡荒野，应对严峻挑战，迎战更多敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/bb406761e648aaf20f3e974f625d8ba5.poster.avif?t=1763116403\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/bb406761e648aaf20f3e974f625d8ba5.webm?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/bb406761e648aaf20f3e974f625d8ba5.mp4?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的派别</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在扎科夫，你会遇到致力于维护法律和秩序的绿衣军，或全球制药和技术巨头赤红公司。作为猎人，你可以选择一个派别，赢得声誉，解锁独特的派别任务，并收集特殊的高级战利品来帮你走过荒野！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/2f83efa1664e81bfb6c202ba284b0d74.poster.avif?t=1763116403\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/2f83efa1664e81bfb6c202ba284b0d74.webm?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/2f83efa1664e81bfb6c202ba284b0d74.mp4?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >猎奇和探寻</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多条任务线引导你穿越《Zero Sievert》的世界。通过与一系列角色的交谈，你将积攒线索，慢慢解开这个世界的传奇秘辛。与此同时，100多种可掠夺的配件能用来制作新道具，升级基地和买卖交易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/d8352240f40ede1999c24dda8e624b83.poster.avif?t=1763116403\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/d8352240f40ede1999c24dda8e624b83.webm?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782120/extras/d8352240f40ede1999c24dda8e624b83.mp4?t=1763116403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模组与 Steam 创意工坊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用 Steam 创意工坊，你可以体验全新的末世扎科夫。在各类改变游戏的模组中，你将能够为武器库引入新武器，了解新派系、新NPC和新任务，使用新的语言，以及更多更新。 </p>",
